Hey lil' coffee beans!!! Mr. State Texas Wedding McGee is back with us this week, and of course there are some interesting stories to tell! But first, a trip down memory lane! Do you remember these iconic gadgets? Are your old toys worth a lot of money? Were the 90s ahead of our time? We have no idea, but it sure is fun to think about. Maybe the luckiest man in the world or the modern day Nikola Tesla has all the answers. Enjoy our low key, wholesome conversation, and comment down below to join us!
